Hello, this is MODHAUS

We regret to inform you that there have been delays in Objekt minting recently, resulting in delays in sending Objekts, distributing COMO, and the Grid. We sincerely apologize for any inconvenience caused. Prior to the Cream01 2nd Edition First Class Objekt sales period, MODHAUS undertook efforts to eliminate any omissions in Objekt minting for a better service experience. While we were able to address all minting omissions, we acknowledge a decrease in minting speed as a consequence. MODHAUS is currently prioritizing the resolution of this issue as our top priority.

We will devote all efforts to achieve a swift resolution.
Thank you.

Hello, this is MODHAUS.
Last Friday, during the minting process of the 2024 tripleS Authentic in Seoul Double Class Objekts, there was an error where 5 Objekts(SooMin, YuBin, Kaede, Kotone, Nien) were minted, skipping specific serial numbers. We apologize for any inconvenience caused. MODHAUS takes this situation seriously and our development team is working hard to stabilize the compensation Objekt drop system. Additionally, we are devising a new method to ensure a more reliable drop of compensation Objekts, which are planned to be implemented in April.We are committed to ensuring a seamless service experience for our users.
We sincerely appreciate your continued interest and support.
Thank you.
